D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10444","headword_ar":"مَخْرَقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaroqN","text_ar":"خَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxoraqu HawoDK","text_ar":"مَخْرَقُ حَوْضٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stone that is at the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euqor","text_ar":"عُقْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hinder part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a watering-trough, for the purpose of their"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"standing upon it, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawing forth the water from it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. the trough,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when they will."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10445","headword_ar":"مَخْرِقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", though unheard by us, is the sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxaAriqu","text_ar":"مَخَارِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"orifices of the body; such as the mouth and the nose and the ears and the anus and the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10446","headword_ar":"مُخْرَقٌ","root":"xrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[pass. part. n. of 4;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Confounded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: and hence,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK: but there written without the vowel of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%85%D8%AE%D8%B1%D9%82/","headword_ar":"مخرق","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_1","lexicon_en":"Ibn Manẓūr, Lisān al-ʿArab (d. 1311 CE)","lexicon_ar":"لسان العرب لابن منظور","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=4293#a03b8d","body_html":"<p>مخرق: المُمَخْرَق: المُمَوَّه، وهي المَخْرقةُ، مأْخوذة من مَخاريق</p><p>الصبيان.</p>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_21","lexicon_en":"Muḥammad al-Fattinī, Majmaʿ Biḥār al-Anwār fī Gharāʾib al-Tanzīl wa Laṭāʾif al-Akhbār (d. 1578 CE)","lexicon_ar":"مجمع بحار الأنوار للفَتِّنيّ","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=4293#68651d","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">[مخرق]</span><span> شا: فيه: بما كان \"يمخرق\" به، بمضمومة فمفتوحة فخاء معجمة ساكنة فراء مكسورة فقاف، أي يختلف ويأتي بأباطيل.</span>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_51","lexicon_en":"Habib Anthony Salmone, An Advanced Learner's Arabic-English Dictionary (1889)","lexicon_ar":"حبيب سالمون، قاموس عربي انجليزي متقدم للمتعلمين","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=4293#be471d","body_html":"مخرق<br> مَخْرَقَ<br> a. Exaggerated.<br> <br> مَخْرَاْقَة<br> (pl.<br> مَخَاْرِيْقُ)<br>a. Exaggerations; bombast; falsehoods; quackery <br> trash.<br> <br> N. Ag.<br> مَخْرَقَa. Impostor; quack."},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_32","lexicon_en":"Supplément aux dictionnaires arabes by Reinhart Dozy (d. 1883 CE)","lexicon_ar":"تكملة المعاجم العربية لرينهارت دوزي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=4293#249928","body_html":"مخرق: مخرق: خرق وخرق (وعند فوك خرق ب وخرق في) مثل خرق بالرمح أي طعن طعنا خفيا. وخرق كذب ولعب كما تلعب الصبيان بالمخاريق. وخرق الثوب شقه وخرق البناء وفي البناء فتح نافذة فيه (م. المحيط. مادة خرق). وخرق فلان أكثر الكذب وخرق الشيء مزقه (م. المحيط مادة خرق).<br>مخرقة: في م. المحيط (بعض العامة يستعمل المخرقة لإلقاء الفساد وتهييج الفتن بين الناس).<br>ممخرق: كذاب (باين سميث) 1037."}]}}